r lsa pre session course windows package installation installing packages on windows up after starting r the first step in installing the packages you will need is to select a cran mirror to download them from when the dialog pops up pick a mirror close to you next go to the install packages menu item under packages find the packages xtable design hmisc languager lme4 e1071 and vr in the list of packages and click on each while holding down the control key hit ok when you re done r will fetch and install them plus all of their dependencies automatically when r finishes downloading and installing the packages you re done
